# Embedded python runtime bundles land here. Built by
# scripts/build-python-runtime-bundle.sh and consumed by go:embed in
# embed_<triple>.go. The bundles are large (~150-250MB) and per-platform;
# CI rebuilds them per matrix leg. Track only this .gitignore so the
# directory exists on a fresh clone.

*.tar.zst
*.sha256
!.gitignore
